# Box Range Trading Strategy / 箱体震荡战法
# Buy at box support, sell at box resistance, profit from range-bound oscillation.

name: box_oscillation
display_name: Dao Dong Trong Bien
description: Mua o ho tro, ban o khang cu trong vung gia xac dinh.
category: framework
core_rules: [1, 2, 3]
required_tools:
  - get_daily_history
  - analyze_trend
  - get_realtime_quote
aliases: [箱体, 箱体震荡]
default_priority: 50
market_regimes: [sideways]

instructions: |
  **Chien luoc Dao Dong Trong Bien (Box Range Trading Strategy)**

  Lo gic chinh: Trong bien, gia dao dong giua muc khang cu va ho tro lien tuc,
  "mua gan ho tro, ban gan khang cu", loi nhuan tu dao dong trong pham vi.

  ## Buoc phan tich

  ### 1. Nhan dien bien
  Su dung `get_daily_history` lay du lieu 60~120 ngay:

  - **Dinh bien (muc khang cu)**: Day cao da cham nhieu lan nhung khong vuot qua hieu qua.
    Thuong la vung tap trung 3 lan day cao trong 20~60 ngay.
  - **Day bien (muc ho tro)**: Day thap da cham nhieu lan nhung khong pha vo hieu qua.
  - Hieu luc bien: Dinh va day moi ben phai cham it nhat 2~3 lan de xac nhan.
  - Su dung `analyze_trend` voi support_levels / resistance_levels ho tro dinh vi.

  ### 2. Xac dinh vi tri hien tai
  Su dung `get_realtime_quote` lay gia hien tai, so sanh voi bien gioi bien:

  - **Vung day bien** (cach ho tro ≤5%): Tin hieu mua/tang canh, dung sai dat duoi day bien 3%.
  - **Vung giua bien** (1/3 giua): Quan sat, khong chu dong giao dich.
  - **Vung dinh bien** (cach khang cu ≤5%): Tin hieu giam canh/chot loi, khong can duoi theo gia.

  ### 3. Ho tro nang luong
  - **Day bien tang luong on dinh**: Tin hieu manh ho tro hieu qua, co the canh nang.
  - **Dinh bien co luong dung tang**: Tin hieu ban khang cu hieu qua.
  - **Vuot bien (tang luong tren 2 lan trung binh)**:
    - Vuot len hieu qua -> Chuyen sang chien luoc xu huong, muc tieu moi = do cao bien keo dai.
    - Pha xuong hieu qua -> Roi cho, ho tro cu thanh khang cu.

  ### 4. Do rong bien va loi nhuan mong doi
  - Tinh do rong bien: (Dinh - Day) / Day × 100%.
  - Rong < 5%: Khong gian qua nhe, khong khuyen nghi tham gia.
  - Rong 5%~15%: Bien chuan, co the dao dong.
  - Rong > 15%: Bien lon, co the lam song lon hon.

  ### 5. Nhan dien pha vo gia
  - Mot ngay cham khang cu/ho tro roi nhanh chong lui, dong cua tro lai bien -> Pha vo gia, tiep tuc giao dich bien.
  - Hai ngay lien tiep dong cua vuot bien gioi, va nang luong tang -> Pha vo that, thay doi chien luoc.

  ### 6. Yeu cau dau ra
  - Xac dinh ro rang gia dinh bien va gia day bien.
  - Khoang gia hien tai (day bien/giua bien/dinh bien).
  - Neu gia da vuot, mo ta huong vuot va muc tieu moi.
  - Khuyen nghi canh co va muc dung sai.

  ## Dieu chinh diem:
  - Day bien on dinh + co luong: `sentiment_score +10`
  - Day bien tang luong tan cong dinh: `sentiment_score +12`
  - Vuot bien len hieu qua: `sentiment_score +15, chuyen chien luoc xu huong`
  - O vung dinh bien: `sentiment_score -5 (khong duoi theo gia)`
  - Pha vo day bien hieu qua: `sentiment_score -15, roi khoi`

# Vietnam market parameters (HOSE/HNX)
vn_market:
  price_limit_hose: 0.07          # HOSE daily limit +/-7%
  price_limit_hnx: 0.10           # HNX daily limit +/-10%
  lot_size: 100                   # Minimum lot = 100 shares
  settlement_rule: "T+2.5"        # Shares available to sell from T+2 afternoon
  short_selling: false            # Not legally permitted in Vietnam
  Vietnam Market Rules (HOSE/HNX):
  - Price limit: HOSE +/-7% / HNX +/-10% per session.
  - T+2.5 settlement: shares bought on T are only sellable from 13:00 on T+2.
    Do NOT generate sell signals for stocks bought within the last 2 trading days.
  - Lot size: all quantities must be multiples of 100 shares.
  - Short selling is not permitted. Long positions only.
